review_text: Cute little space. For 5 years old and younger.
Great little park with climbing structure for the little ones and a bench for Mommy to sit and rest :)

(Translated by Google) Good for children to play!

(Original)
Bom para crianças brincarem!

(Translated by Google) A small park with games for children

(Original)
Un petit parc avec des jeux pour les enfants

(Translated by Google) Well worth the name ... It's not the quantity, it's the quality that counts ...

(Original)
Porte bien son nom... C'est pas la quantité c'est la qualité qui compte...
